11:T466d,<h1>eforge Event Protocol Reference</h1>
<p>All events emitted on the eforge SSE stream conform to the <code>EforgeEvent</code> discriminated
union defined in <code>packages/client/src/events.schemas.ts</code>.</p>
<p>Each event carries an optional envelope (<code>sessionId</code>, <code>runId</code>, <code>timestamp</code>) intersected
with one of the variant objects below. The <code>type</code> field discriminates the variant.</p>
<h2>Event Variants</h2>
<p>Total variants: 150</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Event type</th>
<th>Additional fields</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
